Directed by Jaya Kishore .B.

Written by Jaya Kishore. B

Star Sunny Naveen (Ajay (as Naveen Kumar Reddy)). Seema Chowdary (Anjali). Sammohit Tumuluri (Aanandh Rao). Allu Ramesh (Ram Chandra). Harish Roshan (Bosu). Satish Saripalli (Anjali Father). Leela Venkatesh (Leela)

Language Telugu

Producers Sai Sreekanth Cheruvu. Rajesh Kodepu. Srujan Yarabolu

Production RK Cine Talkies. S Originals
